  "title": "SEIF OS Architecture — Context Daemon Model (3-AI Convergence)",
  "summary": "SEIF OS is NOT a custom OS. It is a context daemon layer running on top of existing operating systems. Proven on macOS (2-machine circuit: Air M1 + Mini M4). Next target: Android (mobility). Architecture: heartbeatd + vigilantd + context-loader + relay as user-space services. Trust: Ed25519 + owner challenge (self-sovereign, no third-party attestation). Mobile hardening via Android Key Attestation (hardware-local). Threat model: data loss, sync corruption, AI drift, human error — NOT APT/zero-day.",
